---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Home">

  <!-- ===== Hero ===== -->
<section class="mb-16">
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-6 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
    <img
      src="/images/profile/me.webp"
      alt="Katsuhiro Yamakawa"
      class="h-20 w-20 shrink-0 rounded-full object-cover sm:h-24 sm:w-24"
    />
    <div class="group">
      <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 sm:text-3xl dark:text-poi-focus">
        Katsuhiro Yamakawa
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-base leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
        Builder / Operator
      </p>
      <p id="coding-since" class="mt-1 font-mono text-xs text-poi-blue opacity-0 transition-opacity duration-500">
        ── coding since 2025.07
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script is:inline>
  const el = document.getElementById('coding-since');
  el?.parentElement?.addEventListener('mouseenter', () => {
    el.style.opacity = '1';
  });
</script>

  <!-- ===== Theme ===== -->
  <section class="mb-16 max-w-3xl">
    <p class="mb-3 text-sm text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent">#human_centric_DX</p>
    <blockquote class="border-l-2 border-light-accent dark:border-poi-accent pl-4">
      <p class="font-sans text-base italic leading-8 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
        The hardest systems to build are the ones that disappear into the background.
      </p>
    </blockquote>
    <p class="mt-5 font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
  <p class="mt-5 font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
  大学を出てからずっと自分で事業をやってきました。<br />
  個人事業、法人設立、そして廃業まで。一通り経験したあとに、コードを書くようになりました。<br />
  現場のバグを経営者目線で見つけ、一度作ったら壊れない、現場に自然に溶け込む仕組み、作ります。
</p>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Works ===== -->
  <section class="mb-16 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Works</h2>
      <a class="cactus-link text-sm" href="/works/">すべて見る →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-6 space-y-4">

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-poi-border dark:bg-poi-panel">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent">現場システム開発</p>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">NFC Attendance System</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          Sony RC-S300 と Raspberry Pi 2 で作った勤怠管理。カードをかざすだけで記録が完結。給与自動計算システム。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline" href="/posts/nfc-attendance-system/">制作記事</a>
          <a class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline" href="https://github.com/yktsnet/nfc-attendance-kit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="rounded-xl border border-zinc-200 bg-white p-5 dark:border-poi-border dark:bg-poi-panel">
        <p class="font-mono text-xs text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent">Web 制作 / SSR Demo</p>
        <h3 class="mt-1 font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-poi-focus">Live Demo (Trading System)</h3>
        <p class="mt-2 font-sans text-sm leading-7 text-zinc-600 dark:text-poi-muted">
          自動売買パイプラインのログを Cloudflare KV 経由で集約し、Astro SSR でリアルタイムに表示するダッシュボード。
        </p>
        <div class="mt-3 flex gap-4 font-mono text-xs">
          <a class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline" href="/live-demo/">Live Demo →</a>
          <a class="text-light-accent dark:text-poi-accent hover:underline" href="/posts/live-demo/">制作記事</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ===== Explore ===== -->
  <section class="mb-14 max-w-3xl">
    <div class="space-y-3">
      <p class="font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
        <a class="cactus-link" href="/posts/">Posts</a>
        <span class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"> — </span>
        設計の背景や判断の理由を書いています。
      </p>
      <p class="font-sans text-base leading-8 text-zinc-700 dark:text-poi-focus/90">
        <a class="cactus-link" href="/contact/">Contact</a>
        <span class="text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400"> — </span>
        お問い合わせ・各種リンク。
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</MainLayout>
